OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781190689
OL,3,CFirefighters on scene after house fire
OL,4,Cspreads to nearby properties
OL,6,FWATCH: Surrey Fire and Rescue crews
OL,7,Fcontinue to put out house fire in
OL,8,FCamberley.
OL,10,FSix fire engines were dispatched in
OL,11,Fthe early hours on Wednesday to stop a
OL,12,Fhouse fire in Surrey, which had spread
OL,13,Fto several neighbouring properties.
OL,15,FCrews from Surrey Fire and Rescue
OL,16,F(SFRS) received a 999 call at 6.02am
OL,17,Fand were sent to Kings Mews, off
OL,18,FFrimley Green Road, in Camberley.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
