CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781190689
OL,3,CFirefighters on scene after house fire
OL,4,Cspreads to nearby properties
OL,6,FThey used an aerial ladder platform,
OL,7,Forganised by a command unit at the
OL,8,Fsite, to put out the fire.
OL,10,FThe incident has since been scaled
OL,11,Fback with only one fire engine and a
OL,12,Fwater carrier at the incident. Footage
OL,13,Ffrom the scene shows nearby roofs
OL,14,Fstill smouldering and one which had
OL,15,Fbeen destroyed.
OL,17,FSFRS said everyone has been accounted
OL,18,Ffor, but it's asking people to
OL,19,Fcontinue to avoid the area while a
OL,20,Fcordon remains in place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
